{"tid":2229488,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"市民再登頂「救港救人」照亮獅子山","createTime":"2020-10-04T12:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T09:01:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8dad9b34d872bc6cf1d05d881d66831d1580d7a9","tid":2229488,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T12:26:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/RK26LLE7PZC5FEJSJKBNBTAX2A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FRK26LLE7PZC5FEJSJKBNBTAX2A%2F&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil6Fdds9vdrezUgVRKRcn1wQ%3D&h=2f084b89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201004%2FRK26LLE7PZC5FEJSJKBNBTAX2A%2F&h=1d1f9960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201004/RK26LLE7PZC5FEJSJKBNBTAX2A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n市民再登頂「救港救人」照亮獅子山<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】十‧一當晚，中秋登山賞月突然成為政府禁忌，警方在獅子山登山口及獅子亭雙重截查阻嚇港人，但仍然無阻登山客的決心，昨日再有一批山友揹着照明器具，一步一攀登，成功於晚上用燈管砌成「SAVE 12」及「SAVE HK」等字句，與山下的萬家燈火相輝映，籲巿民毋忘遭內地當局扣留的12名港人，持續為他們發聲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8wyvRZxndKXBhuLsCs71zJIVv9I=/2658x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TASOYMZNZRFWDCD4OTR44QZQSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8wyvRZxndKXBhuLsCs71zJIVv9I%3D%2F2658x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTASOYMZNZRFWDCD4OTR44QZQSQ.jpg&h=279c5221&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■登山者手持約一米乘一米的燈牌砌出「SAVE HK」字句。謝榮耀攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥中共藉事件威脅港人<br />\n<br />\n昨午5時許，五至六名市民揹着燈管由獅子山燒烤場登山口起步，晚上7時許成功登頂。他們稍作休息後，用燈管砌成「SAVE 12」及「SAVE HK」等字句，每個字母面積達一米乘一米，在漆黑的獅子山頭顯得格外注目，其後他們逐步下山，其間沒有警察在場阻攔。<br />\n<br />\n有參與行動的市民表示，一直有留意12名送中港人的情況，坦言目前港人不單止是被壓迫得失去自由，更是要面對生命危險，「12個可以過中秋嘅人過唔到中秋，佢哋面對緊好大威脅」。他形容，內地政府是試圖借這12人警示及威脅其他港人。他希望透過這次行動呼籲港人堅持下去，同時期盼12人盡快平安回家。<br />\n<br />\n攀登獅子山表達訴求的活動已非首次，十‧一中秋夜有巿民響應網上發起的「和你燈」活動，。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"0f7323e0e029741643780883c4f9d7f7de7f202c","tid":2229488,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T12:27:04.000Z","msg":"12個港人拉鳩左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />救條春咩"},{"pid":"cf829b4112d5c1748104d8fe6bd7e36e87663c62","tid":2229488,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T12:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a038b878ae0b39377872e3113683b8125a9ea2e","tid":2229488,"uid":96327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T12:37:25.000Z","msg":"記得RT<br />\n喂喂喂 唔好淨係話靚先得㗎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2229064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2229064</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"78792baf45ac4b2470f6824bf28301c28d73418b","tid":2229488,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T12:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5757c07522265f86e1ba691097a8e63404a4dc3","tid":2229488,"uid":77526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T10:20:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"534f25b7edf9cc1d583ff686f8327abd74879cfd","tid":2229488,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T10:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062ea8fefb308fa86e4a01d03b09080db8bd677b","tid":2229488,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T08:24:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s